OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family given
OL,4,Cprison sentences for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FFour members of Britain's richest
OL,8,Ffamily have been handed prison
OL,9,Fsentences in Switzerland for
OL,10,Fexploiting servants working in their
OL,11,Fluxury villa.
OL,13,FPrakash Hinduja and his wife, Kamal,
OL,14,Fwere sentenced to four and a half
OL,15,Fyears each, while their son, Ajay, and
OL,16,Fhis wife, Namrata, both received
OL,17,Fsentences of four years in prison.
