OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family given
OL,4,Cprison sentences for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FThe prison sentences have been
OL,8,Fpostponed subject to an appeal lodged
OL,9,Fby the family's lawyers as allowed
OL,10,Funder Swiss law.
OL,12,FThey banned the workers, mostly
OL,13,Filliterate and from India, from
OL,14,Fleaving the villa and forced them to
OL,15,Fwork excruciatingly long days,
OL,16,Fsometimes up to 18 hours.
OL,18,FThe court found the four guilty of
OL,19,Fexploiting the workers, paying them
OL,20,Fwages less than a tenth of the income
OL,21,Ffor domestic work in Switzerland.
