OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family given
OL,4,Cprison sentences for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FEmployees slept in the basement of the
OL,8,Fvilla, in the Cologny neighbourhood of
OL,9,FGeneva, and said Kamal Hinduja
OL,10,Finstilled a "climate of fear".
OL,12,FThey also had their passports seized
OL,13,Fand were paid with rupees into banks
OL,14,Fback home that they could not access.
OL,16,FThe Hindujas moved to Switzerland in
OL,17,Fthe late 1980s. Prakash Hinduja was
OL,18,Fconvicted on less serious but similar
OL,19,Fcharges in 2007.
