OL,7,FAlong with three of of his brothers,
OL,8,FPrakash Hinduja is a leader of an
OL,9,Findustrial conglomerate in sectors
OL,10,Fincluding information technology,
OL,11,Fmedia, power, real estate and
OL,12,Fhealthcare.
OL,14,FSwiss authorities have seized
OL,15,Fdiamonds, rubies, a platinum necklace
OL,16,Fand other assets from the family, as
OL,17,Fthey could be used to pay for legal
OL,18,Ffees and possible penalties.
