OL,7,FWhile announcing they intended to
OL,8,Fappeal, the family's lawyers a
OL,9,Fstatement denying all the allegations
OL,10,Foutlined in the case.
OL,12,FStating they were 'appalled' by the
OL,13,Fcourt's decision, the Hinduja family's
OL,14,Flegal counsel said in a statement:
OL,15,F"Our clients the Hinduja family have
OL,16,Fbeen acquitted of all human
OL,17,Ftrafficking charges.
OL,19,F"The family denies all other charges
OL,20,Fagainst them.
