OL,7,F"As the family are appealing the case,
OL,8,Fthe previous Judgment is not final or
OL,9,Fbinding and the higher court will
OL,10,Frehear the case in its entirety.
OL,12,FUnder the Swiss Code of Criminal
OL,13,FProcedure, the presumption of
OL,14,Finnocence applies until a final
OL,15,Fjudgment by the highest adjudicating
OL,16,Fauthority, which has not yet taken
OL,17,Fplace.
