OL,7,F"Contrary to some media reports, no
OL,8,Fmembers of the family are imprisoned
OL,9,Fas a result of the verdict. The
OL,10,Fcomplainants in this case have
OL,11,Fwithdrawn their civil complaints
OL,12,Fagainst the family.
OL,14,F"The family has full faith in the
OL,15,Fjudicial process and remains confident
OL,16,Fthat the truth will prevail."
